It was a sad tale on Tuesday as three siblings helping their mother shade fresh tomatoes at Sangotedo, Lagos were crushed to death by a truck driver. The accident also claimed the life of a bystander. The Nation gathered that the truck driver, in a bid to avoid running into motorists plying against the traffic swerved towards the victims, killing them in the process. Also, four other persons are feared killed in another accident at Ojodu Bus Stop, Lagos Tuesday afternoon. Details shortlyâ€¦